      <title>香港科学家为濒临灭绝的鲎寻求好运</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/hong-kong-scientists-seek-good-fortune-endangered-horseshoe-crabs-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港自然资源保护主义者周三开始在水下追踪濒临灭绝的鲎（这种鲎的历史可以追溯到恐龙出现之前），以帮助它们在现代生活的危险中生存下来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/hong-kong-scientists-seek-good-fortune-endangered-horseshoe-crabs-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 11:10:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾星宇航空订购 5 架空客 A350 货机、3 架 A330neo</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/taiwans-starlux-airlines-orders-5-airbus-a350-freighters-3-a330neos-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾星宇航空首席执行官周三表示，已订购五架空客 A350 货机和三架 A330neo 宽体客机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/taiwans-starlux-airlines-orders-5-airbus-a350-freighters-3-a330neos-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:23:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>红海弹道导弹袭击引发亚洲对防御的兴趣</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/red-sea-ballistic-missile-attacks-trigger-asian-interest-defences-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[专家和行业官员表示，在红海使用反舰弹道导弹（ASBM）激发了亚洲对用于击落反舰弹道导弹的系统的兴趣，尽管中国拥有庞大的反舰弹道导弹武库，构成了更严峻的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/red-sea-ballistic-missile-attacks-trigger-asian-interest-defences-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 09:39:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾前线渔民对中国紧张局势保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/frontline-taiwan-islands-fishermen-wary-china-tensions-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名中国公民在与台湾海警的追逐中死亡后，中国沿海前线岛屿周围敏感水域的台湾渔民表示，他们担心紧张局势升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/frontline-taiwan-islands-fishermen-wary-china-tensions-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 09:02:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>悉尼武术教练因涉嫌谋杀韩国家庭被捕</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sydney-martial-arts-instructor-arrested-alleged-murder-south-korean-family-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚警方周三表示，一名儿童和一名妇女在跆拳道中心被发现死亡，一名悉尼武术教练因涉嫌三重谋杀一名居住在该市的韩国家庭而被捕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sydney-martial-arts-instructor-arrested-alleged-murder-south-korean-family-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 07:53:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡央行官员：斯里兰卡第三季度至第四季度通胀率将达到 5%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sri-lanka-inflation-reach-5-during-q3-q4-cenbank-official-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡中央银行(CBSL)官员周三表示，随着经济从严重的金融危机中企稳，预计从今年最后两个季度开始，斯里兰卡的通胀率将恢复到政府设定的5%目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sri-lanka-inflation-reach-5-during-q3-q4-cenbank-official-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 07:02:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国有影响力的前总理他信受到柬埔寨老盟友洪森的访问</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-influential-ex-pm-thaksin-gets-visit-old-ally-hun-sen-cambodia-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国颇具影响力的前总理他信·西那瓦本周从拘留中获释，柬埔寨前领导人洪森周三拜访了他信·西那瓦，洪森是这位大亨在自我流放 15 年期间最亲密的盟友之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-influential-ex-pm-thaksin-gets-visit-old-ally-hun-sen-cambodia-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 07:01:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智库称中国儿童保育成本位居全球最高</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-childcare-costs-among-highest-world-think-tank-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国一家著名智库周三表示，相对于人均国内生产总值而言，中国是世界上养育孩子成本最高的国家之一，同时详细介绍了选择在中国生孩子的女性的时间和机会成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-childcare-costs-among-highest-world-think-tank-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 06:58:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡航空前景警告给航展蒙上阴影</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/singapore-airlines-outlook-warning-casts-shadow-over-air-show-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本土航空公司新加坡航空警告称，由于成本上涨，机票价格面临压力，周三该公司股价下跌近 10%，给新加坡航展蒙上了阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/singapore-airlines-outlook-warning-casts-shadow-over-air-show-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 06:24:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国游客涌向东南亚 澳大利亚惨遭淘汰</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-loses-out-chinese-tourists-flock-southeast-asia-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[旅行社和行业数据显示，随着中国游客涌入东南亚免签证国家，澳大利亚正在遭受损失，更多注重成本的大陆游客也选择离家更近、价格更便宜的目的地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-loses-out-chinese-tourists-flock-southeast-asia-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 06:13:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
